$PAR
If the limit of this sequence exists, what is it, otherwise write DNE.
$BR
END_TEXT
Context()->normalStrings;

$q3 = Formula("$a");

Context()->texStrings;
BEGIN_TEXT
\{ ans_rule(20) \}
\{ AnswerFormatHelp("numbers") \}
$PAR
$PAR
Consider the sequence \({\left$LB c^{\sqrt{n}} \right$RB}_{n=1}^\infty\) where \( 0 $LTS c $LTS 1 \text{.}\)
$PAR
If the limit of this sequence exists, what is it, otherwise write DNE.
$BR
END_TEXT
Context()->normalStrings;

$q4 = Formula("0");

